    "description": {
      "value": "<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: justify\">You invoke litanies to Gunndred, calling on him to crush your foes to a pulp. A stampede of bulls, blazing a trail of destruction in their wake, burst from the ground running down anything in their path. Choose one target you can see within 10+Fellowship Bonus yards. All characters within Fellowship Bonus yards of that target are trampled, as are all creatures between the <em>Stampede </em>and the target. Everything that is trampled takes a 1d10+5 Damage hit to the Body (modified normally by Toughness Bonus and Armour Points) as the bulls sink back into the ground. The target location must be outdoors.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">Â </span></p>"
